data.title: Mary O'Donnell - 2011-12 - Women's Basketball
data.meta_description:
Mary O'Donnell (34) Forward  - 

	

	2011-12: Played in 18 games on the year with one start…Scored 15 points on the year with 22 rebounds…Added
data.text:
2011-12: Played in 18 games on the year with one start…Scored 15 points on the year with 22 rebounds…Added two assists and one steal…Tied for fourth on the team with seven blocked shots…Scored season-high six points with three boards against Wentworth on January 14.

2010-11: Played in 17 games on the year…Scored six points and grabbed 13 rebounds…Finished with a four-point, four-rebound performance against Simmons College on December 11.

2009-10: Played in 12 games on the season…Averaged 3.8 minutes per game.

2008-09: Played 16 games on the season…Averaged 1.4 2 points per game and 1.6 rebounds per game.

High School: A 2008 graduate of Mount Alvernia High School…Earned four letters for her efforts as a center on the basketball team…Earned recognition as a Catholic Conference All-Star…Honor Roll Student.
